*cdrtools-2.01_alpha18-r1 (11 Sep 2003)

  11 Sep 2003; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> cdrtools-2.01_alpha18-r1.ebuild:
  Usage of the new USE-flag 'dvdr' which will compile in Mandrake's DVD burner
  patch for using cdrecord with serveral DVD-writers. This ebuild makes
  cdrtools-dvdr obsolete.

